sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as KServe Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Sidecar as Istio Sidecar<br/>mTLS STRICT
    participant vLLM as vLLM HTTP Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant TGIS as vllm_tgis_adapter<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>(S3 / PVC)
    participant GPU as NVIDIA GPU<br/>CUDA

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 1: HTTP Inference Request (OpenAI-compatible)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token / OAuth
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward (mTLS)<br/>HTTP/8000
    Sidecar->>vLLM: HTTP/8000<br/>localhost (no TLS)
    vLLM->>GPU: CUDA inference
    GPU-->>vLLM: Tensor result
    vLLM-->>Sidecar: JSON response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over Client,GPU: Flow 2: gRPC Inference Request (TGIS protocol)
    Client->>Gateway: gRPC GenerationService<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token / OAuth
    Gateway->>Sidecar: Forward (mTLS)<br/>gRPC/8033
    Sidecar->>TGIS: gRPC/8033<br/>localhost (no TLS)
    TGIS->>vLLM: HTTP/8000<br/>localhost bridge
    vLLM->>GPU: CUDA inference
    GPU-->>vLLM: Tensor result
    vLLM-->>TGIS: JSON response
    TGIS-->>Sidecar: gRPC response
    Sidecar-->>Gateway: Response (mTLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response

    Note over vLLM,Storage: Flow 3: Model Loading at Startup
    vLLM->>Storage: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS/443 (S3) or filesystem (PVC)<br/>IAM / service account auth
    Storage-->>vLLM: Model artifacts
    vLLM->>GPU: Load model to VRAM<br/>CUDA memory transfer
